## 2. Request Entry (ServeHTTP)

```go
// gin.go
func (engine *Engine) ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, req *http.Request) {
    engine.routeTreesUpdated.Do(func() { engine.updateRouteTrees() })

    c := engine.pool.Get().(*Context)   // pool-reused Context
    c.writermem.reset(w)
    c.Request = req
    c.reset()                            // index = -1, handlers = nil

    engine.handleHTTPRequest(c)

    engine.pool.Put(c)
}
```

The `Context` starts with `index = -1` (set in `reset()`).

